  "title": "Senior Sales Executive – F&B / Indian Bar",
  "description": "<h3>Job Description</h3><p>We are an Indian bar specialising in authentic Karnataka (Bangalore-style) bar bites and small plates. We are looking for a Senior Sales Executive to drive revenue growth through corporate bookings, events, and strategic partnerships.</p><p>This role involves handling key accounts, mentoring junior sales staff, and supporting sales planning initiatives while maintaining strong client relationships.</p><h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><ul><li><p>Generate and manage sales for corporate bookings, private events, and group reservations</p></li><li><p>Develop and maintain relationships with key corporate and repeat clients</p></li><li><p>Handle complex or high-value sales enquiries and negotiations</p></li><li><p>Support and guide junior sales executives when required</p></li><li><p>Coordinate closely with operations and kitchen teams for event execution</p></li><li><p>Monitor sales performance and contribute to sales planning and forecasting</p></li><li><p>Prepare sales proposals, contracts, and follow-up reports</p></li><li><p>Represent the restaurant at networking or promotional events</p></li></ul><h3>Job Requirements</h3><ul><li><p>Minimum 4–6 years of relevant sales experience, preferably in F&B or hospitality</p></li><li><p>Proven track record in achieving sales targets</p></li><li><p>Strong negotiation, communication, and relationship management skills</p></li><li><p>Ability to work independently with minimal supervision</p></li><li><p>Organised, results-driven, and customer-focused</p></li><li><p>Comfortable handling senior stakeholders and corporate clients</p></li></ul>",
